				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="myModal3" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
	<!--批次合并-->
	<div id="dialog-merge">
		<div class="box-content">
			<div class="control-group">
				<label class="control-label">分类</label>
				<div class="controls">
